<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Beau Merle</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="topmenu">
    <a href="#section0"><img class="logo"  src="/images/logo1.png" alt="Logo Beau Merle"></a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <ul>
          <li><a href="#section0">{% trans %}app.public.menu.accueil{% endtrans %}</a></li>
          <li><a href="#section1">{% trans %}app.public.menu.atelier{% endtrans %}</a></li>
          <li><a href="#thegallery">{% trans %}app.public.menu.galerie{% endtrans %}</a></li>
          <li id="cardsmenu"><a href="#cards">{% trans %}app.public.menu.catalog{% endtrans %}</a></li>
          <li><a href="#infos">{% trans %}app.public.menu.contact{% endtrans %}</a></li>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="{{ path('public.switchlang', { locale: 'en' }) }}">en |</a></li>
            <li><a href="{{ path('public.switchlang', { locale: 'fr' }) }}">fr</a></li>
          </ul>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </nav>
  <div class="allnews">
    <div id="section0" class="news bg-enclume">
      <h1>{% trans %}app.public.main.name{% endtrans %}</h1>
      <h2 >{% trans %}app.public.main.whatis{% endtrans %}</h2>
      <div class="htmltemplate textleft" data-templatename='maintext' data-lang={{locale}}></div>
    </div>
    <div id="section1" class="news bg-thinknife">
      <div class="htmltemplate textleft" data-templatename='story' data-lang={{locale}}></div>
    </div>
    <div id="thegallery">
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="cards" class="cards">
    <div class="cards-header">
      <h1>Les dernières créations</h1>
      <h2>Toutes visibles sur site à Chabreloche !!!</h2>
      <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Velit, nulla corrupti aliquid nihil alias sunt! Impedit sint quidem minima cupiditate dignissimos eveniet ut sit consequuntur ipsam, assumenda aut! Quae amet sequi sapiente nulla, dolores illum quos sint eveniet beatae illo.</p>
    </div>
    <div id="card1" class="cardframe">
      <div class="card-title">Bastoche@work</div>
      <div class="card-image">
        <img src="/images/artisanat.jpg" alt="Avatar">
      </div>
      <div class="card-text">Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Soluta labore vel aut possimus voluptas at eos molestias quisquam, sequi eum in nulla temporibus ut nihil culpa perspiciatis illo enim eveniet! Expedita sint, dolorem odio culpa, vero placeat temporibus molestias aliquam atque nemo velit magnam, quis tempora! Nemo minus doloribus ipsa? Omnis accusantium, at magni mollitia sapiente, beatae consequuntur laboriosam vero excepturi sunt aperiam numquam, autem possimus quisquam? Nam velit ipsum architecto impedit iusto tenetur quo quisquam recusandae quibusdam quidem exercitationem illum ex nihil explicabo eius, quasi minima est deserunt laborum omnis debitis fuga. Laborum nisi tempore beatae expedita, odio voluptates?</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="infos" class="infos">
    <div class="infoelement">
      <h3>{% trans %}contact.infos{% endtrans %}</h3>
      {{ form_start(formcontact, {'attr': {'novalidate': 'novalidate', 'class': 'form'}}) }}
          <div class="contact">
              {{ form_label(formcontact.email, 'contact.email' | trans) }}
              {{ form_widget(formcontact.email) }}
              {{ form_errors(formcontact.email) }}
          </div>
          <div class="contact object">
              {{ form_label(formcontact.object, 'contact.object' | trans) }}
              {{ form_widget(formcontact.object) }}
              {{ form_errors(formcontact.object) }}
          </div>                
          <div class="contact knife">
              {{ form_label(formcontact.reservation, 'contact.couteau' | trans) }}
              {{ form_widget(formcontact.reservation) }}
              {{ form_errors(formcontact.reservation) }}
          </div>
          <div class="contact">
              {{ form_label(formcontact.text, 'contact.message' | trans) }}
              {{ form_widget(formcontact.text) }}
              {{ form_errors(formcontact.text) }}
          </div>
          <button>{% trans %}contact.button{% endtrans %}</button>           
       {{ form_end(formcontact) }}
    </div>
    <div class="infoelement">
        <h3>L'atelier</h3>
        <p>335 Route de Saint-Thomas, Bras de Fer, 63250 Arconsat - France</p>
        <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d22223.601247309492!2d3.6613166626773856!3d45.872306808318406!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x47f6a2cd5cd73055%3A0x4093cafcbe5c880!2s63250%20Chabreloche!5e0!3m2!1sfr!2sfr!4v1694103652086!5m2!1sfr!2sfr" width="600" height="450" style="border:0;" 
                width="350" height="350" 
                style="border:0;" 
                allowfullscreen="" 
                loading="lazy" 
                referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade">
        </iframe>
    </div>
  </div>
  <footer class="footer">
      <img class="menu-hamburger svg-white" src="/images/svg/bars-solid.svg" alt="Show Hide Menu"/>
  </footer>
</div>
</body>

<script src="{{ asset('node_modules/jquery/dist/jquery.min.js')}}"></script>
<script src="{{ asset('scripts/properties.js')}}"></script>
<script src="{{ asset('scripts/dynamic.js')}}"></script>
<script src="{{ asset('scripts/classes/slider.js')}}"></script>
<script src="{{ asset('scripts/classes/gallery.js')}}"></script>
<script src="{{ asset('scripts/classes/card.js')}}"></script>

</html>